  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Lurking Among Shadows</strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3363610/extras/e444075862f6e2cade22a187ff2fedcc.poster.avif?t=1738003070\" width=800 height=352 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3363610/extras/e444075862f6e2cade22a187ff2fedcc.webm?t=1738003070\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3363610/extras/e444075862f6e2cade22a187ff2fedcc.mp4?t=1738003070\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Step into a dark, unsettling forest as Sargent Hawk, a rugged and resourceful survivor doing whatever it takes to make it to the next sunrise. In this tense co-op survival horror, your mission is simple—but nerve-wracking: loot abandoned houses deep in hostile territory to scrape together enough money to survive another day. Players can go explore the forest and bring back the money but if they dont bring enough theyll be left with nothing. Remember to bring your camera, you should capture any suspisous activities at night. The Monsters are scared of the light, but they'll come back. Every creak of the floorboards or rustle of the trees could signal danger, and working together might be the only way to fend off what lurks just out of sight. Will you stick together or risk it alone? In this world the shadows are always watching.<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3363610/extras/1a56b9574fef7dff27b3bd3c18d80f3f.poster.avif?t=1738003070\" width=800 height=352 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3363610/extras/1a56b9574fef7dff27b3bd3c18d80f3f.webm?t=1738003070\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3363610/extras/1a56b9574fef7dff27b3bd3c18d80f3f.mp4?t=1738003070\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Lurking Among Shadows</strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3363610/extras/e444075862f6e2cade22a187ff2fedcc.poster.avif?t=1738003070\" width=800 height=352 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3363610/extras/e444075862f6e2cade22a187ff2fedcc.webm?t=1738003070\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3363610/extras/e444075862f6e2cade22a187ff2fedcc.mp4?t=1738003070\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Step into a dark, unsettling forest as Sargent Hawk, a rugged and resourceful survivor doing whatever it takes to make it to the next sunrise. In this tense co-op survival horror, your mission is simple—but nerve-wracking: loot abandoned houses deep in hostile territory to scrape together enough money to survive another day. Players can go explore the forest and bring back the money but if they dont bring enough theyll be left with nothing. Remember to bring your camera, you should capture any suspisous activities at night. The Monsters are scared of the light, but they'll come back. Every creak of the floorboards or rustle of the trees could signal danger, and working together might be the only way to fend off what lurks just out of sight. Will you stick together or risk it alone? In this world the shadows are always watching.<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3363610/extras/1a56b9574fef7dff27b3bd3c18d80f3f.poster.avif?t=1738003070\" width=800 height=352 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3363610/extras/1a56b9574fef7dff27b3bd3c18d80f3f.webm?t=1738003070\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3363610/extras/1a56b9574fef7dff27b3bd3c18d80f3f.mp4?t=1738003070\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
